  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top"><p class="p1">German made Herbert Richter''s TomTom Go 630, 630T, 720, 720T Global 4 Windscreen Suction Mount, in car holder combo consisting of TomTom Go device specific holder by Herbert Richter with Kickback stand and Herbert Richter Global 4 windscreen suction swivel mount reference&nbsp;1627. The backing mount has a full 360 degrees swivel and an extendible arm allowing you to position your device in perfect viewing angle. This mount can also be used as an excellent dash mount.</p><ul><li class="p2">Device specific holder for the TomTom Go 630, 630T, 720, 720T.</li><li class="p2">Ratcheting plate rotates 360 degrees for perfect viewing position.</li><li class="p2">Extendible arm.</li><li class="p2">Vibration free.</li><li class="p2">Swivel can be tightened with rear side tightening ring.</li><li class="p2">Horizontally and vertically adjustable by 40 degrees.</li><li class="p2">Self-adhesive disk included for use on dashboard</li><li class="p2">Superb suction cups made of plastic material free of DEHP</li><li class="p2">210mm - 240mm x 78mm x 78mm</li><li class="p2">German made</li></ul><p class="p2"><br></p></td>
  </tr>
