    <td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top"><p class="p1">German made Herbert Richter''s TomTom Go 630, 630T, 720, 720T Dual Support Windscreen Suction Mount, in car holder combo consisting of TomTom Go device specific holder by Herbert Richter and Herbert Richter Dual Support Windscreen Suction Swivel Mount&nbsp;reference 1719. Backing dual support mount has a full 360 swivel for positioning your TomTom in perfect viewing angle and can also be used as an excellent dash tower mount.</p><ul><li class="p2">Device specific holder for the TomTom Go 630, 630T, 720, 720T.</li><li class="p2">Ratcheting plate rotates 360 degrees for perfect viewing angle.</li><li class="p2">Vibration free.</li><li class="p2">Swivel can be tightened with rear side tightening ring.</li><li class="p2">Horizontally and vertically adjustable by 40 degrees.</li><li class="p2">Self-adhesive disk included for use on dashboard</li><li class="p2">Superb suction cups made of plastic material free of DEHP</li><li class="p2">167mm x 70mm x 70mm</li><li class="p2">German made</li></ul><p class="p2"><br></p></td>
  </tr>
