<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">This Is Your Edge</span></span></strong></h3>
<p style="border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; margin-bottom: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">The touchscreen Edge 810 is designed for the cyclist who wants it all â navigation and advanced training capabilities in 1 device. It offers connected featuresÂ¹ through your smartphone, including live tracking, social media sharing and weather. The 810 is compatible with optional detailed street or Ordnance SurveyÂ® maps, so it can guide your ride for touring, commuting or extended activities where you might need onboard maps and navigation. Because it''s GPS-enabled, Edge 810 provides accurate data and navigation capabilities, anywhere in the world.</span></span></p>
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><img width="350" height="189" style="margin: 0px; padding: 30px 30px 0px 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 12.72px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; vertical-align: middle; float: right; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);" alt="Edge Web Site" src="https://static.garmincdn.com/en/products/010-01063-00/g/overview/website.jpg"></span></span>
<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Track Every Detail</span></span></strong></h3>
<p style="border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; margin-bottom: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">In addition to the mapping capabilities, Edge 810 records your distance, speed metrics, ascent/descent, grade and more. It''s also compatible with ANT+â¢ sensors that measure your&nbsp;<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 124, 195); line-height: inherit; clear: left; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://buyadmin.garmin.com/shop_stage/shop.do?pID=10996" target="_blank">heart rateÂ²</a>,<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 124, 195); line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://buyadmin.garmin.com/shop_stage/shop.do?pID=1266" target="_blank">speed/cadenceÂ²</a>&nbsp;and powerÂ³. The activity profiles feature allows you to customise data fields and device settings based on cycling activity, such as road, mountain or touring. Switch profiles with a simple swipe of the touchscreen and your device will be set up to show the data you need for that ride.</span></span></p>
<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Get Connected</span></span></strong></h3>
<p style="border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; margin-bottom: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Edge 810 offers a suite of connected features when paired with your smartphone (AppleÂ® or Androidâ¢) and the<a title="Garmin Connect Mobile" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 124, 195); line-height: inherit; clear: left; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://buy.garmin.com/shop/shop.do?pID=125677" target="_blank">Garmin Connect Mobile</a>&nbsp;app. This allows you to gain comprehensive, accurate ride data from a dedicated device, while saving your phone battery. Edge tracks the data and sends it to your phone using a BluetoothÂ® connection. Stay connected and share all the details of your ride with friends, family and your social media contacts. You can post an update immediately after your ride or race with details from your completed activity. You''ll create your posts via your smartphone, and the ride data''s already there, thanks to the interface with&nbsp;<a title="Garmin Connect Mobile" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 124, 195); line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://buy.garmin.com/shop/shop.do?pID=125677" target="_blank">Garmin Connect Mobile</a>.</span></span></p>
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 30px 0px 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 12.72px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; vertical-align: middle; float: left; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);" alt="Live Tracking" src="https://static.garmincdn.com/en/products/010-01063-00/g/overview/phone.jpg"></span></span>
<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Live Tracking</span></span></strong></h3>
<p style="border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; margin-bottom: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">The live tracking feature allows your friends and family to follow your races and training activities in real time. Invite followers using email or social media, so they can view your live data on a Garmin Connect tracking page. Once they get your email invite, they can click to follow and see your stats and location on the map.</span></span></p>
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><img style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 30px 0px 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 12.72px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; vertical-align: middle; float: left; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);" alt="Weather" src="https://static.garmincdn.com/en/products/010-01063-00/g/overview/weather.jpg"></span></span>
<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Weather</span></span></strong></h3>
<p style="border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; margin-bottom: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Get real-time weather conditions, forecasts and alerts directly on the Edge 810 when it''s paired with your smartphone and the&nbsp;<a title="Garmin Connect Mobile" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 124, 195); line-height: inherit; clear: left; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://buy.garmin.com/shop/shop.do?pID=125677" target="_blank">Garmin Connect Mobile</a>&nbsp;app. This feature is useful for extended rides, and it lets you keep your smartphone safe and dry, while the weather data you need is at your fingertips.</span></span></p>
<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 90px 0px 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<strong><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Wireless Data Transfers</span></span></strong></h3>
<p style="border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63px; margin-bottom: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
<span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-family: trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Now you can instantly store, share and analyse every detail of your ride. The&nbsp;<a title="Garmin Connect Mobile" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(0, 124, 195); line-height: inherit; clear: left; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;" href="https://buy.garmin.com/shop/shop.do?pID=125677" target="_blank">Garmin Connect Mobile</a>&nbsp;app allows for wireless uploads of completed activities from your device as soon as you finish recording an activity. You choose whether activities are automatically or manually uploaded. Once your ride has posted to Garmin Connect, your own "connections" can view them. You can also search your courses and workouts<sup style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; top: -0.4em; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 10px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;">4</sup>&nbsp;stored at Garmin Connect, download to your smartphone, then send directly to your Edge 810 â wirelessly. You can then navigate to the start of the course and use the Virtual PartnerÂ® feature on your Edge to race your previous activities in real time.</span></span></p>
<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 1.4; font-family: OpenSansRegular, HelveticaNeue, HelveticaNeueu, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
